Package gameplay.gameboard

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Grid
    Creates a visible grid with the number of rows and columns with the specified arguments
    Obstacle
    Creates a Obstacle, very similar to a unit, but the obstacle has a fixed position, and cannot be damaged or moved by any player.
    PiecePlacer
    This class is used as a placeholder for information stored in database about the opponents units and is used in Database import methods to set up all pieces on the board (Grid)
    Recruit
    Recruit is a own lightweight unit class for avoiding conflicts with the unit class.
    RecruitTile
    Own lightweight version of Tile for use in placementphase for holding recruits.
    Tile
    Creates a Tile to be put inside a Grid.
